- **Blob**: 100GB bandwidth/month
- **KV**: 256MB, 10k commands/day
- Perfect for educational projects!

### Pro Tier ($20/month)
- Everything in Free
- **Postgres**: 512MB storage, 100 hours compute
- Commercial use allowed
